(124, 2056, 'en', 'Figma for UI/UX Designers', 'Master the essential tools and techniques for UI/UX design with Figma', 'Learn how to use Figma to create high-quality UI designs. Discover plugins, shortcuts, and best practices to improve your workflow and efficiency.', '<p>This course will teach you how to use Figma to create high-quality UI designs. You\'ll learn about essential tools and techniques, including plugins, shortcuts, and best practices. By the end of the course, you\'ll be able to use Figma to design professional-level UI and UX.</p><p>The course includes practical exercises and real-world examples to help you apply these skills. You\'ll also learn about the latest features and updates in Figma, and how to stay up-to-date with the design industry.</p><p>Whether you\'re a beginner or an experienced designer, this course will give you the skills and knowledge you need to create stunning UI designs with Figma.</p>'),
